1
00:01:25,360 --> 00:01:29,970
[Coroner's Diary]

2
00:01:30,080 --> 00:01:33,880
[Episode 2]

3
00:01:33,979 --> 00:01:35,900
[Marquis of Anyang's Mansion]

4
00:01:56,979 --> 00:01:57,910
The bride...

5
00:01:58,690 --> 00:02:00,240
Why is the bride beheaded?

6
00:02:08,830 --> 00:02:10,430
-Grandma!
-Are you alright?

7
00:02:12,380 --> 00:02:13,259
Grandma.

8
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:15,410
Bai Feng!

9
00:02:15,440 --> 00:02:17,640
Ladies, bring her back in for some rest.

10
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:19,730
-Hurry. Hold her tight.
-Careful.

11
00:02:20,190 --> 00:02:20,980
Careful.

12
00:02:25,810 --> 00:02:26,580
Rou!

13
00:02:32,590 --> 00:02:33,390
Impossible.

14
00:02:34,910 --> 00:02:36,040
This is impossible.

15
00:02:36,450 --> 00:02:37,710
How could this happen?

16
00:02:38,490 --> 00:02:40,490
I just talked to you this afternoon.

17
00:02:41,310 --> 00:02:42,440
How did this happen?

18
00:02:52,510 --> 00:02:53,600
It must be you.

19
00:02:54,620 --> 00:02:56,770
You were the only stranger
on our way here.

20
00:02:56,770 --> 00:02:58,190
You must've killed Rou!

21
00:02:58,370 --> 00:02:59,180
Ridiculous.

22
00:02:59,600 --> 00:03:00,910
I was asked to welcome the bride

23
00:03:00,910 --> 00:03:02,590
in order to show respect
to the Duke of Song.

24
00:03:02,590 --> 00:03:03,900
I had never met the bride before!

25
00:03:03,900 --> 00:03:04,900
My Lady,

26
00:03:04,930 --> 00:03:05,930
it's time we left.

27
00:03:06,130 --> 00:03:07,220
Not so soon.

28
00:03:07,250 --> 00:03:08,710
It was your job to escort the bride.

29
00:03:08,710 --> 00:03:10,440
Aren't you ashamed to blame me?

30
00:03:10,610 --> 00:03:12,520
The bride died in the wedding sedan.

31
00:03:12,520 --> 00:03:14,579
Don't you think you failed your task?

32
00:03:14,579 --> 00:03:16,050
I grew up with Song Rou.

33
00:03:16,390 --> 00:03:18,050
How could I possibly hurt her?

34
00:03:18,780 --> 00:03:20,730
You must've killed her
because you and your family

35
00:03:20,730 --> 00:03:22,860
are dissatisfied with this marriage!

36
00:03:31,090 --> 00:03:32,690
Why would I be dissatisfied?

37
00:03:32,910 --> 00:03:33,910
If that were true,

38
00:03:34,530 --> 00:03:37,530
why would I welcome the bride
outside the city in person?

39
00:03:37,530 --> 00:03:38,250
Enough.

40
00:03:45,480 --> 00:03:46,200
Bai Feng!

41
00:03:46,630 --> 00:03:48,360
Have the Black Armor Guards
and the guards in the marquis's mansion

42
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:49,760
watch over this area now.

43
00:03:50,020 --> 00:03:51,420
Keep everything intact.

44
00:03:51,910 --> 00:03:52,400
Yes!

45
00:03:53,079 --> 00:03:55,280
Rou hadn't married into
Marquis of Anyang's family yet.

46
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:56,320
Her funeral

47
00:03:57,120 --> 00:03:59,610
should be arranged
by the Duke of Song's family.

48
00:03:59,610 --> 00:04:01,500
I'll take her body back to the capital!

49
00:04:01,500 --> 00:04:02,470
Guards!

50
00:04:05,310 --> 00:04:06,510
Vice Commandant Wei,

51
00:04:06,579 --> 00:04:09,310
The Emperor arranged for Miss Song
to marry Marquis of Anyang's heir.

52
00:04:09,310 --> 00:04:11,960
Her identity was changed
when that decision was made.

53
00:04:11,960 --> 00:04:14,900
Marquis of Anyang's family
will seek justice for her.

54
00:04:14,900 --> 00:04:16,960
All of the bride's escorts, stay put!

55
00:04:17,300 --> 00:04:18,660
No one is allowed to leave

56
00:04:18,660 --> 00:04:20,660
until he is properly interrogated.

57
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:22,090
How dare you?

58
00:04:25,190 --> 00:04:26,350
There is nothing

59
00:04:26,370 --> 00:04:28,300
in the world I dare not do.

60
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:29,540
Take them away!

61
00:04:49,270 --> 00:04:51,610
The bride died on her way
to the groom's home.

62
00:04:51,610 --> 00:04:53,670
Her escorts are the most suspicious.

63
00:04:53,880 --> 00:04:56,540
The Young Marshal of Shuoxi Army
is quite smart.

64
00:04:56,810 --> 00:04:57,500
My Lady,

65
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:59,040
let's go already.

66
00:04:59,340 --> 00:05:01,470
We'll get in trouble if they notice us.

67
00:05:01,610 --> 00:05:04,210
Maybe this is my chance
to make a breakthrough.

68
00:05:09,670 --> 00:05:10,480
Rou,

69
00:05:11,880 --> 00:05:13,159
this is all my fault.

70
00:05:15,880 --> 00:05:17,440
I failed to protect you.

71
00:05:18,130 --> 00:05:19,860
Now, I can't even take you home.

72
00:05:20,550 --> 00:05:22,380
If I had known this would happen,

73
00:05:23,680 --> 00:05:26,210
I wouldn't have insisted on
sending you here.

74
00:05:28,520 --> 00:05:29,310
Jia,

75
00:05:30,310 --> 00:05:31,930
go check on your grandmother.

76
00:05:31,930 --> 00:05:34,290
She must be worried sick about you.

77
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:34,540
[Marquis of Anyang]
[Yue Qiong]

78
00:05:34,540 --> 00:05:35,150
Father,

79
00:05:36,240 --> 00:05:37,040
I'm truly innocent.

80
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:38,820
I know you've been falsely accused.

81
00:05:38,820 --> 00:05:40,880
Before you're cleared of suspicion,

82
00:05:41,420 --> 00:05:43,290
in order to protect the family reputation,

83
00:05:43,290 --> 00:05:46,090
I'm sorry you'll have to
stay at home for a few days.

84
00:05:46,310 --> 00:05:47,110
Do not go out.

85
00:05:51,570 --> 00:05:52,330
Father.

86
00:05:54,850 --> 00:05:56,180
What exactly happened?

87
00:05:56,280 --> 00:05:57,720
The guests are staying
only out of courtesy.

88
00:05:57,720 --> 00:05:59,090
Everyone's asking around chaotically.

89
00:05:59,090 --> 00:06:00,490
Prepare some carriages.

90
00:06:00,540 --> 00:06:03,030
Send all the guests away
through the west door.

91
00:06:03,030 --> 00:06:04,650
Tell them an emergency happened,

92
00:06:04,650 --> 00:06:07,909
and that we'll visit them
and apologize in person someday.

93
00:06:08,200 --> 00:06:08,890
Got it.

94
00:06:13,430 --> 00:06:14,280
Prefect Huo,

95
00:06:14,500 --> 00:06:16,550
the Emperor designated
the bride to be my son's wife.

96
00:06:14,700 --> 00:06:16,620
[Prefect of Jingzhou]
[Huo Huaixin]

97
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:18,230
Her sudden death

98
00:06:18,260 --> 00:06:19,790
is truly heart-wrenching.

99
00:06:20,070 --> 00:06:21,850
This matter involves two noble families.

100
00:06:21,850 --> 00:06:23,320
I hope you will soon

101
00:06:23,640 --> 00:06:24,970
identify the murderer.

102
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:26,190
Rest assured, Your Grace.

103
00:06:26,190 --> 00:06:28,640
I'll get to the bottom of this case.

104
00:06:43,080 --> 00:06:45,870
Vice Commandant Wei, please calm down.

105
00:06:45,890 --> 00:06:49,420
Your cooperation is required
for the upcoming investigation.

106
00:06:52,210 --> 00:06:53,370
Prefect Huo,

107
00:06:53,710 --> 00:06:55,600
do you take me as a suspect now?

108
00:06:56,140 --> 00:06:56,670
No, no.

109
00:06:56,700 --> 00:06:58,190
I was ordered by the Duke of Song

110
00:06:58,190 --> 00:07:00,390
to escort Rou through a long distance
to the groom's home.

111
00:07:00,390 --> 00:07:01,920
She was fine and healthy
on the whole trip.

112
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:04,390
Yet she died upon reaching Jingzhou. Why?

113
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:07,870
Obviously, the Yue family
intentionally caused her death.

114
00:07:07,870 --> 00:07:09,360
Prefect Huo, shouldn't you

115
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:10,720
give me an explanation?

116
00:07:10,720 --> 00:07:12,510
Sir, please don't take me wrong.

117
00:07:12,510 --> 00:07:14,460
I assure you I will handle the case justly

118
00:07:14,460 --> 00:07:16,260
and reveal the truth.

119
00:07:17,130 --> 00:07:17,960
Prefect Huo.

120
00:07:18,070 --> 00:07:19,870
Interview the bride's escorts right away.

121
00:07:19,870 --> 00:07:21,040
Do not miss any of them!

122
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:21,680
Yes.

123
00:07:22,840 --> 00:07:25,960
Vice Commandant Wei,
please go home and get some rest.

124
00:07:29,850 --> 00:07:31,200
All the bride's escorts,

125
00:07:31,200 --> 00:07:32,880
get up and come with me!

126
00:07:46,640 --> 00:07:47,720
Hurry. Hurry up.

127
00:07:47,960 --> 00:07:48,450
Keep up!

128
00:07:51,159 --> 00:07:52,020
Your Highness.

129
00:07:52,140 --> 00:07:53,640
You came just in time, Prefect Huo.

130
00:07:53,640 --> 00:07:55,820
The wedding sedan
and her body should be

131
00:07:55,820 --> 00:07:57,280
taken away for examinations soon.

132
00:07:57,280 --> 00:08:00,150
Your Highness,
I've made arrangements in that respect.

133
00:08:00,150 --> 00:08:02,690
Now, the priority is
to interrogate the suspects.

134
00:08:02,690 --> 00:08:05,450
Your Highness,
please keep watch on this place.

135
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:10,810
Why doesn't the prefect

136
00:08:10,830 --> 00:08:13,159
have the wedding sedan
and the body examined first?

137
00:08:13,159 --> 00:08:14,770
If any evidence gets damaged,

138
00:08:14,770 --> 00:08:16,140
he'll be held liable.

139
00:08:16,490 --> 00:08:17,720
What a fool.

140
00:08:17,750 --> 00:08:19,870
My Lady, don't meddle with this.

141
00:08:19,890 --> 00:08:21,600
What if the Grand Princess
knows that you, a girl,

142
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:22,680
do a coroner's work

143
00:08:22,710 --> 00:08:23,980
and hates you for it?

144
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:25,850
Then no one will have our backs.

145
00:08:25,880 --> 00:08:28,120
It won't happen.
Solving this case will do good

146
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:29,660
to me and the Marquis of Anyang's family.

147
00:08:29,660 --> 00:08:30,510
Don't worry.

148
00:08:39,130 --> 00:08:39,760
Master.

149
00:08:40,110 --> 00:08:40,750
Bai Feng,

150
00:08:41,040 --> 00:08:42,820
order the Black Armor Guards
to patrol in shifts.

151
00:08:42,820 --> 00:08:44,680
Go and dismiss anyone who lingers,

152
00:08:44,680 --> 00:08:47,030
inquires or peeks
near the wedding sedan

153
00:08:47,049 --> 00:08:47,900
and the walls.

154
00:08:48,130 --> 00:08:49,070
But don't hurt them.

155
00:08:49,070 --> 00:08:49,760
Yes!

156
00:08:50,090 --> 00:08:51,150
Circle up the area!

157
00:08:51,210 --> 00:08:52,039
Yes!

158
00:09:05,240 --> 00:09:06,760
Black Armor Guards, listen!

159
00:09:06,760 --> 00:09:08,090
Turn your backs to the wedding sedan!

160
00:09:08,090 --> 00:09:08,890
Yes!

161
00:09:57,720 --> 00:09:58,650
This is odd.

162
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:01,680
Suppose the bride was beheaded in here,

163
00:10:01,680 --> 00:10:03,330
her blood would spurt out

164
00:10:03,900 --> 00:10:06,170
and reach the top of the wedding sedan.

165
00:10:06,690 --> 00:10:07,770
But the bloodstains on the top,

166
00:10:07,770 --> 00:10:09,650
the curtains and the window frame

167
00:10:10,370 --> 00:10:11,730
are pointed on the end

168
00:10:11,760 --> 00:10:13,620
and long like cast-off patterns.

169
00:10:21,370 --> 00:10:23,830
Those on the bride's collar
also seem wrong.

170
00:10:23,850 --> 00:10:25,310
If she was hacked to death,

171
00:10:25,390 --> 00:10:27,400
shouldn't there have been more blood left?

172
00:10:27,400 --> 00:10:29,400
But now, only the collar is stained.

173
00:10:35,180 --> 00:10:35,820
I see.

174
00:10:36,270 --> 00:10:38,210
The wedding sedan
cannot be the murder scene.

175
00:10:38,210 --> 00:10:39,320
I'm afraid the traces here

176
00:10:39,320 --> 00:10:40,080
were faked.

177
00:10:40,080 --> 00:10:40,910
You guys,

178
00:10:40,910 --> 00:10:42,440
take the body to the morgue,

179
00:10:42,560 --> 00:10:44,920
and the wedding sedan
to the prefect's office.

180
00:10:44,920 --> 00:10:45,590
Don't!

181
00:10:49,450 --> 00:10:50,450
Miss Qin?

182
00:10:50,960 --> 00:10:52,240
[Huo Ning]

183
00:10:51,200 --> 00:10:52,530
What are you doing here?

184
00:10:52,940 --> 00:10:53,690
Gentlemen,

185
00:10:54,080 --> 00:10:56,560
please leave the body
and the wedding sedan be.

186
00:10:56,560 --> 00:10:58,960
They can't be moved before being examined.

187
00:10:59,920 --> 00:11:01,540
This is an official investigation.

188
00:11:01,540 --> 00:11:03,030
A woman such as yourself

189
00:11:03,060 --> 00:11:03,960
had better keep quiet

190
00:11:03,960 --> 00:11:04,820
and go away now.

191
00:11:04,860 --> 00:11:06,260
Moving the wedding sedan

192
00:11:06,280 --> 00:11:08,130
and the body before examining them

193
00:11:08,130 --> 00:11:09,990
will inevitably cause damage
to the evidence.

194
00:11:09,990 --> 00:11:12,710
Can you bear the consequences, gentlemen?

195
00:11:13,760 --> 00:11:14,660
Miss Qin,

196
00:11:15,020 --> 00:11:16,730
as a young maiden,

197
00:11:16,850 --> 00:11:19,920
don't you know what it means
to be reverent and obedient?

198
00:11:19,920 --> 00:11:22,440
By openly interfering with
our work as officers,

199
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:25,670
your family will be criticized
for not educating you well, won't it?

200
00:11:25,670 --> 00:11:26,900
Mr. Huo, I didn't realize

201
00:11:26,900 --> 00:11:29,440
that you're so familiar
with female precepts.

202
00:11:29,440 --> 00:11:32,010
Now I understand why you're still
unaware of the importance of examinations

203
00:11:32,010 --> 00:11:33,790
despite Prefect Huo's enduring tutoring.

204
00:11:33,790 --> 00:11:35,720
It turns out that he raised you as a girl,

205
00:11:35,720 --> 00:11:37,210
based on your aptitude.

206
00:11:37,650 --> 00:11:38,170
You...

207
00:11:39,810 --> 00:11:41,450
Who's laughing? Who?

208
00:11:41,470 --> 00:11:42,170
Don't laugh!

209
00:11:42,170 --> 00:11:42,790
I'm not laughing.

210
00:11:42,790 --> 00:11:43,510
Shut up!

211
00:11:46,180 --> 00:11:46,970
Qin Wan,

212
00:11:47,070 --> 00:11:47,920
I know

213
00:11:48,630 --> 00:11:49,630
you still resent my family

214
00:11:49,630 --> 00:11:51,550
for breaking off our engagement.

215
00:11:51,850 --> 00:11:53,830
But pestering me like this

216
00:11:53,860 --> 00:11:55,340
won't change my mind.

217
00:11:55,760 --> 00:11:57,400
You'd better give up now.

218
00:11:58,090 --> 00:11:59,660
Hearing what you said,

219
00:11:59,680 --> 00:12:00,990
I feel so relieved.

220
00:12:01,540 --> 00:12:03,600
Thank you for not changing your mind.

221
00:12:03,600 --> 00:12:06,270
Otherwise, I really don't know
how to face my late father.

222
00:12:06,270 --> 00:12:07,240
-Let’s go.
-You…

223
00:12:07,570 --> 00:12:08,570
Y-Y-You...

224
00:12:10,010 --> 00:12:11,010
She truly left.

225
00:12:12,280 --> 00:12:13,740
What did she discover just now?

226
00:12:13,740 --> 00:12:15,140
What are you waiting for?

227
00:12:15,330 --> 00:12:16,460
Where's the ox cart?

228
00:12:16,560 --> 00:12:18,610
Move this stuff right away!

229
00:12:19,210 --> 00:12:20,270
Without the young marshal's permission,

230
00:12:20,270 --> 00:12:21,930
no one can approach the scene!

231
00:12:23,270 --> 00:12:23,720
I...

232
00:12:23,990 --> 00:12:24,790
It's alright.

233
00:12:28,270 --> 00:12:29,080
Mr. Huo.

234
00:12:30,190 --> 00:12:31,210
My name is Huo Ning.

235
00:12:31,210 --> 00:12:32,360
Greetings, Your Highness.

236
00:12:32,360 --> 00:12:33,150
Are you the examiner

237
00:12:33,150 --> 00:12:34,610
appointed by Prefect Huo?

238
00:12:35,110 --> 00:12:37,200
My father only asked me
to move the wedding sedan

239
00:12:37,200 --> 00:12:39,390
to the prefect's office
and her body to the morgue.

240
00:12:39,390 --> 00:12:42,480
Other officers and the coroner
will conduct examinations.

241
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:43,860
Is this the standard procedure

242
00:12:43,860 --> 00:12:45,390
in every local government?

243
00:12:45,900 --> 00:12:46,860
To my knowledge,

244
00:12:46,890 --> 00:12:47,760
yes.

245
00:12:48,160 --> 00:12:51,510
What if the testimonies don't
match the examination results?

246
00:12:51,510 --> 00:12:53,600
The testimonies prevail, of course.

247
00:12:53,600 --> 00:12:55,000
Examination results...

248
00:12:56,530 --> 00:12:58,530
They're not always accurate.

249
00:13:01,910 --> 00:13:02,960
The Black Armor Guards will escort you

250
00:13:02,960 --> 00:13:05,160
to the prefect's office and the morgue.

251
00:13:05,240 --> 00:13:06,640
Stay cautious on the way.

252
00:13:06,760 --> 00:13:08,640
Do not lose or omit any items.

253
00:13:08,940 --> 00:13:10,400
Before the case is solved,

254
00:13:10,420 --> 00:13:11,680
you'll all stay there.

255
00:13:11,900 --> 00:13:12,450
Yes!

256
00:13:27,160 --> 00:13:28,050
My Lady,

257
00:13:28,480 --> 00:13:30,570
please stay away from that case.

258
00:13:31,130 --> 00:13:33,770
Luckily, the Black Armor Guards
didn't notice us tonight.

259
00:13:33,770 --> 00:13:34,920
What if they had caught us

260
00:13:34,920 --> 00:13:37,000
and found out your real identity?

261
00:13:38,090 --> 00:13:39,780
You saved the Grand Princess's life.

262
00:13:39,780 --> 00:13:41,990
We can ask her to send us to the capital.

263
00:13:43,000 --> 00:13:45,200
My father's good name has been smeared.

264
00:13:45,280 --> 00:13:47,310
I have no one to rely on in the capital.

265
00:13:47,310 --> 00:13:49,040
I can't even find out the truth.

266
00:13:49,360 --> 00:13:51,510
How am I supposed
to clear my father's name?

267
00:13:51,510 --> 00:13:53,110
But you have medical skills.

268
00:13:53,550 --> 00:13:55,910
If we save more nobles' lives
in the capital,

269
00:13:55,910 --> 00:13:56,480
then we...

270
00:13:56,480 --> 00:13:58,940
Nobles don't always
fall ill on the streets.

271
00:13:59,520 --> 00:14:01,720
Since I knew my father had been framed,

272
00:14:02,280 --> 00:14:05,440
it has taken me much time
to realize what I should do.

273
00:14:06,550 --> 00:14:08,020
I'll have the Grand Princess

274
00:14:08,020 --> 00:14:09,650
trust my skills as a coroner

275
00:14:09,680 --> 00:14:11,700
just like she trusts my medical expertise.

276
00:14:11,700 --> 00:14:15,130
