280
00:14:20,480 --> 00:14:22,500
I will become the first female coroner

281
00:14:22,500 --> 00:14:24,500
who puts all men to shame.

282
00:14:24,960 --> 00:14:25,790
But...

283
00:14:26,200 --> 00:14:27,440
This case about a headless bride

284
00:14:27,440 --> 00:14:29,270
involves noble families.

285
