286
00:14:31,130 --> 00:14:33,770
What if the Duke of Song or Prefect Huo

287
00:14:33,910 --> 00:14:35,340
is discontent with your work...

288
00:14:35,340 --> 00:14:37,220
I don't need to please everyone.

289
00:14:37,370 --> 00:14:38,370
In matters of criminal justice,

290
00:14:38,370 --> 00:14:40,430
it's impossible to please everyone.

291
00:14:41,320 --> 00:14:43,580
All I need is the Grand Princess's trust.

292
00:14:43,770 --> 00:14:45,770
My father taught me autopsy skills.

293
00:14:46,080 --> 00:14:47,800
I'll clear my parents' names

294
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:49,750
with my own capability.

295
00:14:50,450 --> 00:14:51,710
I'll bring the killers

296
00:14:51,890 --> 00:14:54,080
of them and Qin Liang to justice.

297
00:14:54,460 --> 00:14:56,440
