298
00:14:56,440 --> 00:14:57,770
to accomplish all that.

299
00:14:58,230 --> 00:14:59,660
I''ll do whatever you say, My Lady.

300
00:14:59,660 --> 00:15:00,590
If you don't fear,

301
00:15:00,590 --> 00:15:01,720
then I don't either.

302
00:15:07,480 --> 00:15:08,610
What have you found?

303
00:15:08,840 --> 00:15:11,040
Is Qin Wan really Qin Liang's daughter?

304
00:15:11,720 --> 00:15:12,380
Yes, she is.

305
00:15:12,720 --> 00:15:13,720
Our intelligence shows

306
00:15:13,720 --> 00:15:16,050
that Qin Wan is Qin Liang's only daughter.

307
00:15:16,250 --> 00:15:17,440
She was born with poor health.

308
00:15:17,440 --> 00:15:18,530
She lost her mother at six,

309
00:15:18,530 --> 00:15:20,200
and was then sent to
the Medicine King Valley for treatment.

310
00:15:20,200 --> 00:15:21,770
She didn't leave until
she recovered a year ago.

311
00:15:21,770 --> 00:15:24,170
There's nothing unusual
about her background.

312
00:15:24,170 --> 00:15:26,890
Only commoners can stay
in that valley for treatment.

313
00:15:26,890 --> 00:15:28,560
Any disclosure of patients' information
is forbidden there.

314
00:15:28,560 --> 00:15:30,570
Even our spies
can't infiltrate that place.

315
00:15:30,570 --> 00:15:32,650
Why could she stay there
for over ten years?

316
00:15:32,650 --> 00:15:35,410
It's said that Qin Liang had no interest
in working as an official.

317
00:15:35,410 --> 00:15:36,440
He was obsessed with medicine,

318
00:15:36,440 --> 00:15:38,410
and often provided people
with free medical service.

319
00:15:38,410 --> 00:15:39,930
People call him "Dr. Virtue."

320
00:15:39,930 --> 00:15:42,010
The Medicine King Sun Xi
and he were good friends.

321
00:15:42,010 --> 00:15:43,320
The former would certainly

322
00:15:43,320 --> 00:15:45,250
accommodate a bosom friend's daughter.

323
00:15:45,250 --> 00:15:46,250
What a shock

324
00:15:46,250 --> 00:15:47,930
