of Prince Jin's case.

337
00:16:12,720 --> 00:16:14,180
Now, only Shen Yi can prove

338
00:16:14,440 --> 00:16:16,970
that Consort Jin wasn't killed
by Prince Jin.

339
00:16:17,590 --> 00:16:18,940
I don't believe a man like Prince Jin

340
00:16:18,940 --> 00:16:21,070
would flee out of fear for punishment.

341
00:16:22,290 --> 00:16:24,260
Track down Shen Yi
and his family at all costs.

342
00:16:24,260 --> 00:16:25,900
Find them, or their bodies.

343
00:16:26,320 --> 00:16:27,290
As for Qin Wan,

344
00:16:28,600 --> 00:16:29,650
I'll investigate her myself.

345
00:16:29,650 --> 00:16:30,860
Miss Qin saved

346
00:16:31,240 --> 00:16:32,770
the Grand Princess's life.

347
00:16:33,080 --> 00:16:34,280
Why investigate her?

348
00:16:34,720 --> 00:16:36,380
Because I need her expertise.

349
00:16:36,930 --> 00:16:37,800
If she's clean,

350
00:16:38,200 --> 00:16:39,200
she'll be a strong aide

351
00:16:39,200 --> 00:16:41,660
for our investigation
of Prince Jin's case.

352
00:16:41,840 --> 00:16:43,040
Can you believe this?

353
00:16:43,080 --> 00:16:45,080
A parentless girl traveled a long way

354
00:16:45,080 --> 00:16:47,080
to bring her father's coffin home
after staying in a valley for years.

355
00:16:47,080 --> 00:16:49,940
She keeps composed,
though under her uncle's roof.

356
00:16:50,320 --> 00:16:52,960
