409
00:19:11,640 --> 00:19:12,970
Who do you think you are?

410
00:19:13,000 --> 00:19:14,280
How dare you curse her

411
00:19:14,310 --> 00:19:15,440
in broad daylight?

412
00:19:16,040 --> 00:19:16,940
I dare not.

413
00:19:17,090 --> 00:19:19,570
I spoke out of turn
in the heat of the moment.

414
00:19:19,790 --> 00:19:21,240
Your words carry no grace.

415
00:19:21,240 --> 00:19:22,680
What's the point of a having a tongue?

416
00:19:22,680 --> 00:19:23,740
Cut her tongue off!

417
00:19:28,050 --> 00:19:29,150
Please spare my life, Your Ladyship!

418
00:19:29,150 --> 00:19:30,520
I won't do wrong again!

419
00:19:30,610 --> 00:19:32,780
Grandma, please help me!

420
00:19:36,370 --> 00:19:38,630
Princess Yongning, please don't be mad.

421
00:19:39,090 --> 00:19:41,470
I did a terrible job disciplining her.

422
00:19:41,760 --> 00:19:45,170
That's why she appears so rebellious.

423
00:19:45,480 --> 00:19:46,680
I beg

424
00:19:47,000 --> 00:19:48,400
Your Ladyship to forgive

425
00:19:48,760 --> 00:19:50,200
this young and ignorant girl.

426
00:19:50,200 --> 00:19:53,660
I'll give her severe punishment
according to the family rules

427
00:19:53,850 --> 00:19:55,310
as a warning to the others.

428
00:19:55,720 --> 00:19:57,680
I beg Your Ladyship.

429
00:19:59,680 --> 00:20:00,960
According to the rules of the Qin family,

430
00:20:00,960 --> 00:20:02,170
