434
00:20:18,570 --> 00:20:20,370
That's too many. It'll kill her.

435
00:20:20,480 --> 00:20:21,120
Make it 20.

436
00:20:22,140 --> 00:20:23,650
Thanks, Your Highness.

437
00:20:24,520 --> 00:20:25,280
Take her out.

438
