482
00:22:11,440 --> 00:22:13,810
I'm willing to assist the prefect
in solving this case

483
00:22:13,810 --> 00:22:16,410
to help the Grand Princess relieve
her anxiety as soon as possible.

484
00:22:16,410 --> 00:22:17,520
Forensic skills?

485
00:22:18,320 --> 00:22:18,920
It's to...

486
00:22:18,960 --> 00:22:20,530
It's to examine corpses

487
00:22:20,760 --> 00:22:23,480
to determine the cause and time
of death and other things

488
00:22:23,480 --> 00:22:25,740
in order to help catch the real culprits.

489
00:22:26,240 --> 00:22:27,090
Your Highness,

490
00:22:27,090 --> 00:22:29,000
are you afraid that my practice
of forensic skills

491
00:22:29,000 --> 00:22:30,130
