493
00:22:31,890 --> 00:22:33,490
You're just too impressive!

494
00:22:36,440 --> 00:22:37,640
Speaking of bad luck,

495
00:22:37,680 --> 00:22:39,680
for families
with military backgrounds like ours,

496
00:22:39,680 --> 00:22:42,610
