551
00:25:18,760 --> 00:25:19,170
Let's go.

552
00:25:19,170 --> 00:25:20,170
I won't blame him.

553
00:25:25,610 --> 00:25:27,250
Greetings, Your Highness.

554
00:25:27,330 --> 00:25:29,040
Greetings, Your Highness.

555
00:25:29,240 --> 00:25:31,970
Prefect Huo, there's no need
for such formality.

556
00:25:32,610 --> 00:25:35,410
I think I saw this lady yesterday.

557
00:25:35,720 --> 00:25:37,330
This is Miss Qin from the Qin family,

558
00:25:37,330 --> 00:25:37,930
Qin Wan.

559
00:25:40,950 --> 00:25:42,320
Greetings, Lord Huo.

560
00:25:42,610 --> 00:25:44,900
So you're Miss Qin from the Qin family.

561
00:25:45,570 --> 00:25:47,930
Miss Qin has some insights
into the bride case.

562
00:25:47,930 --> 00:25:49,570
She hopes to assist you.

563
00:25:50,730 --> 00:25:51,650
Miss Qin.

564
00:25:52,280 --> 00:25:53,720
Now that you've met the prefect,

565
00:25:53,720 --> 00:25:55,380
why don't you speak your mind?

566
00:25:55,550 --> 00:25:56,310
Yue Ning.

567
00:26:02,060 --> 00:26:04,190
Sir, have you found the victim's head?

568
00:26:04,370 --> 00:26:05,340
Not yet.

569
00:26:05,370 --> 00:26:06,890
Have you examined the wedding sedan?

570
00:26:06,890 --> 00:26:09,610
I've asked people to search it
thoroughly three times.

571
00:26:09,610 --> 00:26:11,610
The wedding sedan
was even dismantled into planks.

572
00:26:11,610 --> 00:26:14,470
But we still haven't found any trace
of the head yet.

573
00:26:14,960 --> 00:26:15,760
Lord Huo.

574
00:26:15,890 --> 00:26:18,440
Could you allow me to read
the coroner's report?

575
00:26:18,440 --> 00:26:20,680
The coroner's report
is an official document.

576
00:26:20,680 --> 00:26:22,830
Not everyone can have access to it.

577
00:26:23,040 --> 00:26:23,690
It's fine.

578
00:26:24,330 --> 00:26:25,190
Let her read it.

579
00:26:26,000 --> 00:26:26,720
Yes.

580
00:26:37,390 --> 00:26:38,760
In this report,

581
00:26:38,780 --> 00:26:40,810
why is there no record
of examining the corpse?

582
00:26:40,810 --> 00:26:42,250
If the head hasn't been found,

583
00:26:42,250 --> 00:26:43,520
how can you confirm that

584
00:26:43,520 --> 00:26:45,380
the victim is the bride, Song Rou?

585
00:26:46,240 --> 00:26:48,460
Who else could be the bride
if it was not Song Rou?

586
00:26:48,460 --> 00:26:50,370
Perhaps Duke of Song didn't want to
marry off his daughter,

587
00:26:50,370 --> 00:26:52,170
so he sent a substitute bride there.

588
00:26:52,170 --> 00:26:54,630
Perhaps in order to
confuse us, the murderer

589
00:26:54,680 --> 00:26:56,370
sent a headless female corpse there.

590
00:26:56,370 --> 00:26:58,170
Currently,
there's no evidence showing that

591
00:26:58,170 --> 00:27:00,000
the victim is Song Rou, the only

592
00:27:00,000 --> 00:27:02,060
legitimate daughter of Duke of Song.

593
00:27:02,480 --> 00:27:05,520
Vice Commandant Wei, who escorted
the bride there, has confirmed it.

594
00:27:05,520 --> 00:27:07,720
How did Vice Commandant Wei confirm it?

595
00:27:08,120 --> 00:27:09,850
How could there be any mistake?

596
00:27:10,000 --> 00:27:11,720
Before we can catch the murderer,

597
00:27:11,720 --> 00:27:13,410
all escort guards related to the victim

598
00:27:13,410 --> 00:27:14,210
are suspects.

599
00:27:14,440 --> 00:27:16,330
Their statements cannot be trusted.

600
00:27:16,330 --> 00:27:18,040
To confirm the identity of the victim,

601
00:27:18,040 --> 00:27:20,280
Lord Huo, please examine the corpse
as soon as possible.

602
00:27:20,280 --> 00:27:22,760
Even ordinary people don't want
their own bodies to be damaged,

603
00:27:22,760 --> 00:27:24,960
not to mention that the victim
has such noble status.

604
00:27:24,960 --> 00:27:28,330
How could those lowly coroners
desecrate her body?

605
00:27:28,330 --> 00:27:29,890
Although coroners are lowly workers,

606
00:27:29,890 --> 00:27:30,890
an autopsy is the key

607
00:27:30,890 --> 00:27:33,000
to determining life or death,
conviction or acquittal,

608
00:27:33,000 --> 00:27:34,610
and the mechanism for justice.

609
00:27:34,610 --> 00:27:36,330
Sir, if you make such hasty judgments,

610
00:27:36,330 --> 00:27:37,610
aren't you afraid of biased investigations

611
00:27:37,610 --> 00:27:38,890
leading to wrongful convictions?

612
00:27:38,890 --> 00:27:40,650
W-Well...

613
00:27:40,650 --> 00:27:41,680
Y-You....

614
00:27:41,680 --> 00:27:43,560
You're just talking nonsense!

615
00:27:43,930 --> 00:27:46,130
Your Highness,
I've been an official for many years,

616
00:27:46,130 --> 00:27:48,650
and I've never wrongly convicted anyone.

617
00:27:48,650 --> 00:27:50,280
Prefect Huo, you're overthinking it.

618
00:27:50,280 --> 00:27:51,560
Miss Qin didn't mean that.

619
00:27:51,560 --> 00:27:52,910
I did indeed mean that.

620
00:27:53,000 --> 00:27:55,600
Your Highness, there's no need
to cover for me.

621
00:27:55,600 --> 00:27:57,280
Matters of criminal justice

622
00:27:57,850 --> 00:28:00,330
are not for a lady to speak of recklessly.

623
00:28:00,820 --> 00:28:03,780
Miss Qin, please watch your tongue.

624
00:28:03,850 --> 00:28:05,550
A sage of criminal law once said,

625
00:28:05,550 --> 00:28:08,580
"Errors in prison cases often arise
from initial misjudgments."

626
00:28:08,580 --> 00:28:09,650
Lord Shen Yi

627
00:28:09,720 --> 00:28:11,890
once revised "The Washing Away of Wrongs"
at the Supreme Court,

628
00:28:11,890 --> 00:28:13,040
citing numerous real cases

629
00:28:13,040 --> 00:28:14,440
and confirming the importance
of autopsies.

630
00:28:14,440 --> 00:28:16,380
Now without even confirming
the identity of the victim,

631
00:28:16,380 --> 00:28:17,930
are you just rushing to conclusions?

632
00:28:17,930 --> 00:28:20,280
Shen Yi? He was an imperial criminal

633
00:28:20,280 --> 00:28:22,810
and was sentenced to execution
of his entire clan.

634
00:28:22,810 --> 00:28:24,850
You regard such a disloyal
and treacherous person

635
00:28:24,850 --> 00:28:25,960
as a role model?

636
00:28:26,090 --> 00:28:27,650
That's just too...

637
00:28:28,310 --> 00:28:29,350
imprudent, huh?

638
00:28:39,720 --> 00:28:41,280
I'm a sheltered lady.

639
00:28:41,570 --> 00:28:43,680
I don't understand the changing tides
of the imperial court.

640
00:28:43,680 --> 00:28:46,410
I only know "The Washing Away of Wrongs"
revised by the Supreme Court

641
00:28:46,410 --> 00:28:48,340
is the masterpiece of Lord Shen Yi.

642
00:28:48,890 --> 00:28:50,760
It was also once used as a classic book
at the Ministry of Justice

643
00:28:50,760 --> 00:28:53,810
and was promoted to officials
in various places for practical use.

644
00:28:53,810 --> 00:28:56,240
I guess you've read it too, huh?

645
00:28:57,300 --> 00:28:58,430
So what?

646
00:29:01,520 --> 00:29:02,810
I truly cannot bear

647
00:29:03,090 --> 00:29:04,150
to see the murderer

648
00:29:04,570 --> 00:29:06,200
take advantage of your kindness

649
00:29:06,200 --> 00:29:07,530
and manipulate the law.

650
00:29:08,570 --> 00:29:10,680
If you don't blame me for acting
beyond my authority,

651
00:29:10,680 --> 00:29:13,170
I'm willing to help you
investigate the cause of her death

652
00:29:13,170 --> 00:29:14,500
to ease people's minds.

653
00:29:15,650 --> 00:29:16,930
Can you really do it?

654
00:29:19,890 --> 00:29:21,890
Miss Qin is known as the medical fairy.

655
00:29:21,890 --> 00:29:23,810
Determining the cause of death
isn't difficult for her.

656
00:29:23,810 --> 00:29:25,540
If you have no other solutions,

657
00:29:25,610 --> 00:29:27,130
why don't you let her give it a try?

658
00:29:27,130 --> 00:29:29,090
There happens to be a murder case
at the morgue.

659
00:29:29,090 --> 00:29:30,680
I can let her give it a try.

660
00:29:31,160 --> 00:29:32,820
If she's really capable of it,

661
00:29:33,040 --> 00:29:35,680
I'll let her investigate
the new bride case.

662
00:29:45,570 --> 00:29:46,520
Coroner Xu.

663
00:29:47,040 --> 00:29:49,760
Lin Daxing was beaten to death
by the foreman, Wei Wu.

664
00:29:49,760 --> 00:29:51,680
Why did you only examine
the victim's body?

665
00:29:51,680 --> 00:29:54,200
And why didn't you check
whether his internal organs were damaged?

666
00:29:54,200 --> 00:29:57,930
Then you just concluded that the victim
died from a hidden disease?

667
00:29:58,000 --> 00:30:00,130
I'm inexperienced in the profession.

668
00:30:00,280 --> 00:30:02,570
I've never performed autopsies before.

669
00:30:03,440 --> 00:30:05,440
You don't know how to perform autopsies?

670
00:30:05,440 --> 00:30:06,810
How did you become a coroner?

671
00:30:06,810 --> 00:30:08,070
Didn't you tell me that

672
00:30:08,200 --> 00:30:10,720
I didn't need to learn, just like you?

673
00:30:12,720 --> 00:30:15,330
Wei Wu's description of the fight

674
00:30:15,330 --> 00:30:17,930
matches
the coroner's examination perfectly.

675
00:30:17,930 --> 00:30:21,040
If there's no fatal external injury,
there must be a hidden disease.

676
00:30:21,040 --> 00:30:22,900
So there's no need for an autopsy.

677
00:30:22,960 --> 00:30:24,860
If the victim died from a hidden disease,

678
00:30:24,860 --> 00:30:26,660
what's the cause of his disease?

679
00:30:28,040 --> 00:30:29,850
As a prefect,

680
00:30:30,370 --> 00:30:31,300
how would I know?

681
00:30:31,520 --> 00:30:33,680
Indeed, you don't need to
know these things.

682
00:30:33,680 --> 00:30:35,650
Since I've suggested re-examining
the cause of his death,

683
00:30:35,650 --> 00:30:37,850
I will surely handle the case to the end.

684
00:30:39,850 --> 00:30:41,240
How will you re-examine it?

685
00:30:41,240 --> 00:30:43,200
I will personally perform
an autopsy on the body.

686
00:30:43,200 --> 00:30:44,120
-What?
-What?

687
00:31:12,120 --> 00:31:14,180
What are these for?

688
00:31:14,410 --> 00:31:16,500
Taking fragrant pills
and Atractylodes water

689
00:31:16,500 --> 00:31:18,110
can help to remove the corpse odor

690
00:31:18,110 --> 00:31:20,040
and protect us from corpse toxins.

691
00:31:23,610 --> 00:31:26,610
Igniting valerian is for avoiding
pathogenic filth.

692
00:31:38,590 --> 00:31:39,460
Take a pill.

693
00:31:50,760 --> 00:31:52,960
Is there anything wrong
with the hand protection cloth?

694
00:31:52,960 --> 00:31:54,520
This stuff is not waterproof.

695
00:31:54,520 --> 00:31:55,680
During the autopsy,

696
00:31:55,680 --> 00:31:58,810
the hands will probably
be injured by the corpse fluids.

697
00:32:13,390 --> 00:32:16,050
No noise is allowed
during the autopsy. Get out.

698
00:32:18,910 --> 00:32:19,670
Let's go.

699
00:32:28,440 --> 00:32:30,900
All unnecessary personnel shall step back.

700
00:32:32,380 --> 00:32:33,030
Xu He.

701
00:32:33,350 --> 00:32:35,180
Write down every word I say.

702
00:32:35,200 --> 00:32:35,900
Yes.

703
00:32:51,310 --> 00:32:52,240
Write this down.

704
00:32:52,440 --> 00:32:53,750
The victim, Lin Daxing,

705
00:32:53,750 --> 00:32:55,870
male, is about 5 feet 6 inches tall.

706
00:32:57,570 --> 00:32:58,670
His entire body is swollen

707
00:32:58,670 --> 00:33:00,200
and is full of livor mortis.

708
00:33:08,960 --> 00:33:10,220
There's a loss of hair.

709
00:33:11,760 --> 00:33:12,820
He has bulging eyes

710
00:33:13,370 --> 00:33:14,610
and slightly parted lips.

711
00:33:14,610 --> 00:33:17,940
There are dark brown blood clots
between the lips and teeth.

712
00:33:26,760 --> 00:33:29,020
There are maggots in his seven orifices.

713
00:33:32,720 --> 00:33:34,880
I think he died
during the summer months.

714
00:33:34,880 --> 00:33:36,040
About five days ago.

715
00:33:39,680 --> 00:33:42,080
There are clear blood stains
on his wounds.

716
00:33:45,800 --> 00:33:49,200
There's a circular blue-black
blood stain on his left chest.

717
00:33:49,680 --> 00:33:52,540
No record was made
during the initial examination.

718
00:33:52,990 --> 00:33:53,790
Write it down.

719
00:34:06,100 --> 00:34:08,500
Why are they rinsing
the corpse with water?

720
00:34:11,850 --> 00:34:12,600
Fu Ling.

721
00:34:12,850 --> 00:34:14,300
Fu Ling, come on! Hurry up!

722
00:34:14,300 --> 00:34:16,630
Little Wan'er is dissecting the corpose.

723
00:34:21,840 --> 00:34:22,440
Lord Huo.

724
00:34:22,720 --> 00:34:25,520
Did Miss Qin really cut open
the corpse's abdomen?

725
00:34:26,380 --> 00:34:28,710
What does it look like inside the abdomen?

726
00:34:29,080 --> 00:34:29,960
Alright.

727
00:34:29,960 --> 00:34:32,159
I won't ask anymore. Go ahead and vomit.

728
00:34:36,639 --> 00:34:38,230
Is Chi doing this on purpose?

729
00:34:38,230 --> 00:34:39,690
Why is he blocking my view?

730
00:34:43,850 --> 00:34:45,980
Even Coroner Xu is vomiting like this.

731
00:34:46,370 --> 00:34:48,429
What exactly is Little Wan'er doing?

732
00:34:48,520 --> 00:34:49,600
Stop looking.

733
00:35:17,800 --> 00:35:18,430
Scissors.

734
00:35:58,430 --> 00:35:59,690
The heart is ruptured.

735
00:35:59,740 --> 00:36:01,400
I found the cause of his death.

736
00:36:01,440 --> 00:36:02,120
Xu He.

737
00:36:03,560 --> 00:36:04,690
He went out to vomit.

738
00:36:06,290 --> 00:36:07,820
How long have you been here?

739
00:36:08,240 --> 00:36:09,840
I've been here all this time.

740
00:36:10,610 --> 00:36:11,400
Oh, no.

741
00:36:11,690 --> 00:36:13,320
Was he testing me just now?

742
00:36:13,620 --> 00:36:15,680
Has he already started to suspect me?

743
00:36:15,930 --> 00:36:18,120
Why did I wipe her sweat just now?

744
00:36:18,600 --> 00:36:20,400
I hope she won't misunderstand.

745
00:36:23,380 --> 00:36:24,440
Your Highness.

746
00:36:24,790 --> 00:36:26,180
It's not good to let others know

747
00:36:26,180 --> 00:36:27,610
I'm skilled at autopsies.

748
00:36:27,610 --> 00:36:29,210
Please keep this secret for me.

749
00:36:29,210 --> 00:36:29,880
Alright.

750
00:36:33,750 --> 00:36:35,000
-Miss Qin.
-Little Wan'er.

751
00:36:35,000 --> 00:36:36,730
Thank you for your hard work.

752
00:36:39,480 --> 00:36:40,690
I've found out that

753
00:36:40,910 --> 00:36:42,160
the victim, Lin Daxing,

754
00:36:42,160 --> 00:36:44,670
was struck by a round blunt object
on the left side of his chest

755
00:36:44,670 --> 00:36:46,210
and died from heart ruptures.

756
00:36:46,210 --> 00:36:47,880
His Highness didn't mind the filth

757
00:36:47,880 --> 00:36:49,940
and has finished the autopsy report.

758
00:36:51,600 --> 00:36:52,210
Lord Huo.

759
00:36:52,560 --> 00:36:54,850
If we send people to search
Wei Wu's house now,

760
00:36:54,850 --> 00:36:55,760
I think we'll be able to find

761
00:36:55,760 --> 00:36:58,120
the murder weapon
that matches the chest wound.

762
00:36:58,120 --> 00:37:00,850
However, the weapon
was probably wrapped in cotton cloth.

763
00:37:00,850 --> 00:37:02,060
That was why during the
initial examination,

764
00:37:02,060 --> 00:37:03,930
there were no obvious external wounds.

765
00:37:03,930 --> 00:37:06,910
The injuries only became apparent
after the body had deteriorated.

766
00:37:06,910 --> 00:37:08,830
I'll go ask people to search for it now.

767
00:37:08,830 --> 00:37:09,630
Wait.

768
00:37:12,060 --> 00:37:14,260
If it weren't for Miss Qin's help today,

769
00:37:14,440 --> 00:37:16,700
the murderer would have escaped easily.

770
00:37:16,820 --> 00:37:17,820
Guys, please

771
00:37:18,210 --> 00:37:20,470
don't tell others about today's autopsy

772
00:37:20,480 --> 00:37:23,540
so that Miss Qin won't be slandered
by ignorant people.

773
00:37:24,020 --> 00:37:25,680
Your Highness, you're right.

774
00:37:26,240 --> 00:37:27,700
Thank you, Your Highness.

775
00:37:28,510 --> 00:37:29,770
It's just a small matter.

776
00:37:29,770 --> 00:37:31,300
No need for such formality.

777
00:37:32,460 --> 00:37:34,230
Miss Qin's autopsy this time

778
00:37:34,250 --> 00:37:36,280
has helped Jingzhou catch the culprit
and uphold justice.

779
00:37:36,280 --> 00:37:39,220
I really don't know
how to express my gratitude.

780
00:37:39,460 --> 00:37:41,160
If you truly want to thank me,

781
00:37:41,430 --> 00:37:43,540
why don't you go back and copy ten times

782
00:37:43,540 --> 00:37:46,800
"The Washing Away of Wrongs"
revised by the Supreme Court?

783
00:37:48,300 --> 00:37:49,750
I was just joking.

784
00:37:49,970 --> 00:37:51,410
Please don't take it seriously.

785
00:37:51,410 --> 00:37:52,730
Just learn your lesson from this case.

786
00:37:52,730 --> 00:37:53,520
What a joke!

787
00:37:53,520 --> 00:37:54,420
What a joke!

788
00:37:54,450 --> 00:37:56,780
From now on, I won't ignore

789
00:37:56,800 --> 00:37:58,030
autopsies anymore.

790
00:37:59,110 --> 00:37:59,770
Chi.

791
00:38:00,220 --> 00:38:01,640
Little Wan'er is so impressive.

792
00:38:01,640 --> 00:38:04,840
Why don't you let her be the coroner
for the new bride case?

793
00:38:07,070 --> 00:38:09,330
I wonder what Lord Huo thinks about that.

794
00:38:09,330 --> 00:38:11,160
Miss Qin excels in
both medicine and forensics.

795
00:38:11,160 --> 00:38:12,800
It would be my honor.

796
00:38:13,220 --> 00:38:15,400
I'll send people to arrest Wei Wu now.

797
00:38:15,490 --> 00:38:16,260
I'll

798
00:38:16,690 --> 00:38:17,820
take my leave first.

799
00:38:23,580 --> 00:38:25,910
Fortunately, I didn't fail in my mission.

800
00:38:25,990 --> 00:38:27,600
I surely won't let you down.

801
00:38:28,200 --> 00:38:29,030
What about me?

802
00:38:29,480 --> 00:38:30,420
What can I do?

803
00:38:33,990 --> 00:38:35,390
Think about what I can do.

804
00:38:43,820 --> 00:38:45,420
What are you thinking about?

805
00:38:46,000 --> 00:38:46,950
My Lady.

806
00:38:47,210 --> 00:38:48,470
Don't you think

807
00:38:48,770 --> 00:38:51,170
you trust Prince Chi a bit too much?

808
00:38:53,080 --> 00:38:54,330
I don't trust him.

809
00:38:54,360 --> 00:38:55,690
I just need his support.

810
00:38:55,930 --> 00:38:59,000
But he's the current Emperor's nephew.

