00:38:59,290 --> 00:39:01,440
If he finds out
about your identity, then...

812
00:39:01,440 --> 00:39:03,700
I've always been cautious around him.

813
00:39:03,830 --> 00:39:05,410
I don't think he can find any flaws.

814
00:39:05,410 --> 00:39:06,090
Besides,

815
00:39:06,210 --> 00:39:07,590
who says that someone skilled in forensics

816
00:39:07,590 --> 00:39:09,560
must be a daughter of the Shen family?

817
00:39:09,560 --> 00:39:11,880
So, that's a good thing?

818
00:39:11,910 --> 00:39:14,130
Yes. With our current situation,

819
00:39:14,410 --> 00:39:15,960
the more support we have, the better.

820
00:39:15,960 --> 00:39:17,420
The stronger, the better.

821
00:39:21,960 --> 00:39:22,730
Bai Feng.

822
00:39:24,840 --> 00:39:25,840
I'm here.

823
00:39:25,870 --> 00:39:27,030
What are your orders, Master?

824
00:39:27,030 --> 00:39:28,760
Bring me all of Shen Yi's books.

825
00:39:29,640 --> 00:39:31,170
Why do you need those books?

826
00:39:32,700 --> 00:39:34,550
I want to examine
his writings and statements

827
00:39:34,550 --> 00:39:36,420
to investigate the truth
behind his reputation

828
00:39:36,420 --> 00:39:38,750
and figure out
why she respects him so much

829
00:39:39,000 --> 00:39:42,330
and why she's so interested in
matters of criminal justice.

830
00:39:42,380 --> 00:39:44,310
He, he, he, she?

831
00:39:45,100 --> 00:39:47,190
The "she" refers to Miss Qin, right?

832
00:39:48,250 --> 00:39:50,110
Do you have feelings for Miss Qin?

833
00:39:54,970 --> 00:39:55,780
Bai Feng.

834
00:39:57,290 --> 00:39:59,350
The moonlight is beautiful tonight.

835
00:39:59,510 --> 00:40:01,930
Go to the Marquis Mansion's
training ground.

836
00:40:01,930 --> 00:40:04,740
He, he, he, she.

837
00:40:05,790 --> 00:40:06,460
40 laps.

838
00:40:06,740 --> 00:40:07,260
Go.

839
00:40:08,220 --> 00:40:08,950
Well, Master...

840
00:40:08,950 --> 00:40:09,550
50 laps.

841
00:40:10,560 --> 00:40:11,080
Yes.

842
00:40:20,770 --> 00:40:21,440
Mother.

843
00:40:23,930 --> 00:40:24,530
Mother.

844
00:40:25,250 --> 00:40:26,310
Please drink more.

845
00:40:26,460 --> 00:40:27,540
Yes, Grandma.

846
00:40:27,600 --> 00:40:28,660
Please drink more.

847
00:40:29,790 --> 00:40:31,100
Is there any news

848
00:40:33,530 --> 00:40:34,780
about Song Rou?

849
00:40:38,200 --> 00:40:39,920
Prefect Huo is investigating the case.

850
00:40:39,920 --> 00:40:40,690
Grandma.

851
00:40:41,080 --> 00:40:42,600
Little Wan'er has said that now you should

852
00:40:42,600 --> 00:40:44,270
avoid worrying and tiring yourself.

853
00:40:44,270 --> 00:40:45,500
Is there any news?

854
00:40:46,410 --> 00:40:47,290
Mother.

855
00:40:47,890 --> 00:40:49,440
Please focus on your recovery now.

856
00:40:49,440 --> 00:40:51,960
How can you expect me
to focus on my own recovery?

857
00:40:51,960 --> 00:40:52,960
It concerns

858
00:40:53,530 --> 00:40:55,590
the eldest grandson of the Yue family

859
00:40:55,890 --> 00:40:58,000
and the entire Yue clan.

860
00:40:58,270 --> 00:41:00,500
If His Majesty blames us,

861
00:41:00,520 --> 00:41:02,810
which member
of our Marquis of Anyang's Mansion

862
00:41:02,810 --> 00:41:04,120
can bear the responsibility?

863
00:41:04,120 --> 00:41:04,960
Can you?

864
00:41:05,290 --> 00:41:06,290
Can you?

865
00:41:06,860 --> 00:41:07,890
Who can?

866
00:41:14,490 --> 00:41:15,570
Mother.

867
00:41:16,220 --> 00:41:17,010
Mother.

868
00:41:18,230 --> 00:41:19,060
Grandma!

869
00:41:19,460 --> 00:41:20,590
-Grandma!
-Mother!

